<ArticleLayout
  title="Intermittent Fasting: The Gender Gap in Science"
  description="Intermittent fasting was sold as a universal metabolic upgrade, but the core research largely excluded premenopausal women. New evidence reveals a distinct hormonal risk profile that the IF consensus was never designed to catch."
  category="Nutrition"
